<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <script defer src="/index.js"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"> 
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin> 
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand&family=Roboto+Slab:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="logo">
        <img class="logo--img"
          src="/images/JL_Logo_blue&orange._91d1d7&e27458 Medium.jpeg"
          alt="logo"
        />
      </div>
      <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="toggle navigation">
        <span class="hamburger"></span>
      </button>
      <nav class="nav">
        <ul class="nav__list">
          <li class="nav__item">
            <a href="/" class="nav__link">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav__item">
            <a href="#services" class="nav__link">My services</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav__item">
            <a href="#about" class="nav__link">About me</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav__item">
            <a href="#work" class="nav__link">My work</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- introduction -->
    <section class="intro" id="home">
      <h1 class="section__title section__title--intro">
        Hi, I am <strong>Jane Liang </strong>
      </h1>
      <p class="section__subtitle section__subtitle--intro">
        Aspiring Full-Stack Web Developer
      </p>
      <img
        class="intro__img"
        src="/images/me2.jpeg"
        alt="a picture of Jane smiling"
      />
    </section>

    <!-- my section -->
    <section class="my-services" id="services">
      <h2 class="section__title section__title--services">What I do</h2>
      <div class="services">
        <div class="service">
          <h3>Web Design</h3>
          <p>
            Disigning is the first step of building a website and I am highly interested in this creative 
            step of Full-Stack web-development. A website should not only have an apealing look, it also
            needs to tell a great story. 
          </p>
          </div>

          <div class="service">
          <h3>Web Development</h3>
          <p>
            There are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available, but
            the majority have suffered alteration in some form, by injected
            humour, or randomised words which don't look even slightly
            believable. If you are going to use a passage of Lorem Ipsum, you
            need to be sure there isn't anything embarrassing hidden in the
            middle of text. All the Lorem Ipsum generators on the Internet tend
            to repeat predefined chunks as necessary.
          </p></div>

          <div class="service">
          <h3>Database</h3>
          <p>
            Database stores all the information of your users, customers, and inventories ect. A good 
            designed database will keep all your informatin well organized and easy maintain.
          </p>
        </div>

    </div>
    <a href="#work" class="btn">My Work</a>
    </section>
    <!-- about me -->
    <section class="about-me" id="about">
      <h2 class="section__title section__title--about">Who I am</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle section__subtitle--about">
        Aspiring Full-Stack Web Developer graduating in 2023
      </p>

      <div class="about-me__boby">
        <p>
          I am currently a Full-Stack Web Development student at BCIT (British
          Columbia Institute of Technology). This is a 2 years program, and I am currently in the second year.
          <!-- When it comes to make something practical and beatiful, I always present my full passion into building the products that would make usersâ€™ life better.  -->
        </p>

        <p>
          My first exposure to coding was when I took the OAT
          (Office Administrator with Techknowledgy) program at BCIT. In this
          program, I became a certified specialist with Microsoft Office suite.
          More importantly, I learned some basic Front-end programming in HTML
          and CSS. This helped me discover my inner passion for programming.
        </p>
        <!-- link to idsp project -->
        <p>
          After two years of working in the office environment, I finally made the
          decistion to start my coding career in September of 2021. After one
          year of intense learning and training, I not only learned
          web-development skills, but also learned to be collaborative,
          displined, hard working, and meeting deadlines. By practicing the IDSP
          (interdisciplinary student projects), I applied all I have learned
          in school materials and also gained so much new knowledge from
          building full websites. It taught me that if I believe I can do
          somthing, I can!
        </p>

        <p>
         I am open to join a fun and creative team to apply my coding
        skills.
        </p>
      </div>

      <img
        class="about-me__img"
        src="/images/me-lipstic.jpeg"
        alt="my dressed in suit"
      />
    </section>

    <!-- my work -->

    <section class="my-work" id="work">
      <h2 class="section__title">My Work</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle">A selection of my range of work</p>

      <div class="allCard">
     <% for (const project of allProjects) {%>
        <div class="card">
        <a class="image-box" href="/project/<%=project.id%>">  
          <img class="project-image" src="<%= project.images[0]%>"> 
          <span class="show-detail">Click to see project detail</span>
        </a>
        <a class="project-name" href="<%=project.url%>">  
          <%= project.name%> 
          <span class="hover-show">
            <%if(project.url){%>
            <%=project.url%>
            <%}%>
          </span>
        </a>
        </div>
        <%}%>
      </div>

    </section>

    <footer class="footer">

      <div class="contact-me white-background">
        <ul class="list">
          <li>
            <img class="contact-icon" src="/icons/email.svg" />
            <a href="mailto:janeliangbc@gmail.com" class="contact email-link">janeliangbc@gmail.com</a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <img class="contact-icon" src="/icons/phone.svg" />
            <p class="contact phone-number">7787085905</p>
          </li>

          <li>
            <img class="contact-icon" src="/icons/linkedin.svg" />
            <a href="www.linkedin.com/in/janiejane" class="contact linkedin-link">www.linkedin.com/in/janiejane</a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <img class="contact-icon" src="/icons/github.svg" />
            <p class="contact github-name">Cocoandjane</p>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="buttons">
        <button class="download download-resume">
            <img class="download-icon" src="/icons/download.svg" alt="downlaod icon"> Download my resume
        </button>

        <button class="download download-portfolio">
            <img class="download-icon" src="/icons/download.svg" alt="downlaod icon"> Download this portfolio as PDF
        </button>
      </div>
      <img class="footer__img" src="/images/me-footer.jpeg">
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
